name: Nena Trinity (Gundam00) LoRA
description:
General Info

This LoRA has been trained using the Anything v4.5 model. It does a great job at generating characters that look almost exactly like Nena Trinity from the Mobile Suit Gundam 00 series. It seems to be rather easy to put her into different clothes and settings using this LoRA as it has very been trained on her face very exactly. This is mostly an sfw model so nsfw capabilities could be there but have not been tested.

Usage

The model has been trained using Kohya so you probably want to use it in the same way as you use other Kohya models. If you are Using A1111's Webui you want to move the file into the models>Lora directory. It is very important to use the relevant trigger word so that you can get results that look close to mine or even better.
